<title>USA: ForeFront posts Aug loss after acquisition.</title>
<headline>ForeFront posts Aug loss after acquisition.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1996-10-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>ForeFront Group Inc said Friday that after its acquisition of AllMicro Inc, it recorded a net loss of about $300,000 on revenues of about $1.4 million in August.</p>
<p>The results include the operations of AllMicro, which was acquired in July for one million shares of ForeFront common stock.  The transaction cost about $1.6 million, which will be recorded as operating expense in the quarter ended September 30.</p>
<p>AllMicro has since been renamed ForeFront Direct.</p>
